thout needing prior approval. This decision follows concerns raised by developers and engineers about potential hazards. Owners of low-rise buildings can also proceed with construction and repairs. The revised notification aims to ensure site safety and prevent structural issues.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/kolkata-civic-body-resumes-construction-for-g4-buildings-prioritizing-safety-critical-works/132253150?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-925329/132253150.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}